      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't want to bother my doctor over just a headache. it's not like i'm having a crisis or anything. i just need something to take the pain away so i can get through the day. can i just take a standard dose like 200mg? it shouldn't do much harm if it's just a one time thing.",
