      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i hear you but i really can't get a hold of anyone right now and i'm honestly just struggling to function. is there nothing else i can take? maybe like a little extra tylenol or a different brand? i just need something that works and won't mess up my kidneys so i can stop feeling like this.",
